    "mimeType": "text/markdown",
    "content": "# tn-bubble-box Bubble Box\n\n---\ncategory: action\ntitle: Bubble Box / 气泡框\ncomponent-dir: bubble-box\nprimary-tags:\n  - tn-bubble-box\nrelated-tags: []\nstatus: stable\nsource-dir: node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/bubble-box\nstyle-source:\n  - node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/bubble-box.scss\ndemo-pages:\n  - src/demo-pages/component/bubble-box/index.vue\n---\n\n## Component Role\n\n`tn-bubble-box` is a small popover menu that anchors to trigger content and\nshows one or more lightweight actions.\n\n## Best Fit Scenarios\n\n- contextual overflow menus\n- small operation lists next to a button or text trigger\n- popover-style action hints with icons\n- lightweight anchored menus that should not cover the whole screen\n\n## Avoid Using It For\n\n- long action lists\n- destructive or high-stakes confirmations\n- full-screen mobile menus where `action-sheet` is clearer\n\n## Recommended Repo Usage\n\n```vue\n<tn-bubble-box :options=\"bubbleOptions\">\n  点击弹出气泡框\n</tn-bubble-box>\n```\n\n## Key Capabilities\n\n### Menu Model\n\n- `options` array with `text`, `icon`, and `disabled`\n- `click` event for option selection\n\n### Position And Style\n\n- `position` such as `top`, `bottom`, `left`, and `right`\n- `bg-color`\n- `text-color`\n- `width`\n- `option-item-padding`\n\n## Boundary With Similar Components\n\n- use `bubble-box` for anchored micro-menus\n- use `action-sheet` for bottom-sheet action menus\n- use `popup` when the content body needs full custom layout\n\n## AI Usage Notes\n\n- keep the option count very small\n- prefer bubble-box when the action set belongs to a nearby trigger\n- use icons only when they improve recognition, not as decoration\n- verify outside-click close behavior and exact event payloads from source\n\n## Related Demos\n\n- `src/demo-pages/component/bubble-box/index.vue`\n\n## Drill-Down Paths\n\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/bubble-box/src/bubble-box.vue`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/bubble-box/src/bubble-box.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/bubble-box/src/types.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/bubble-box/src/instance.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/bubble-box.scss`\n\n## Evidence Status\n\n- Demo confirmed:\n  - `src/demo-pages/component/bubble-box/index.vue`\n- Source paths mapped:\n  - `components/bubble-box/src/bubble-box.vue`\n  - `components/bubble-box/src/bubble-box.ts`\n  - `components/bubble-box/src/types.ts`\n- Still verify in source:\n  - exact click payload structure\n  - close behavior and slot customization surface\n"
