    "description": "tn-circle-progress Circle Progress",
    "mimeType": "text/markdown",
    "content": "# tn-circle-progress Circle Progress\n\n---\ncategory: display\ntitle: Circle Progress / 圆形进度条\ncomponent-dir: circle-progress\nprimary-tags:\n  - tn-circle-progress\nrelated-tags: []\nstatus: stable\nsource-dir: node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/circle-progress\nstyle-source:\n  - node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/circle-progress.scss\ndemo-pages:\n  - src/demo-pages/component/progress/index.vue\n---\n\n## Component Role\n\n`tn-circle-progress` is a circular percentage indicator for centered progress\ndisplay.\n\n## Best Fit Scenarios\n\n- card-based progress summaries\n- metrics dashboards\n- upload or task completion shown as a circular gauge\n\n## Avoid Using It For\n\n- dense list rows with limited horizontal space\n- indefinite loading states\n- ordered multi-step processes\n\n## Recommended Repo Usage\n\n```vue\n<tn-circle-progress :percent=\"50\" />\n```\n\n## Key Capabilities\n\n### Progress Display\n\n- `percent`\n- `show-percent`\n\n### Visual Controls\n\n- `radius`\n- `ring-width`\n- `inactive-color`\n- `active-color`\n\n## Boundary With Similar Components\n\n- use `circle-progress` when the progress indicator itself is a focal element\n- use `line-progress` for inline or dense layouts\n- use `count-to` when the core message is a changing number rather than a ring\n\n## AI Usage Notes\n\n- keep radius and ring width proportionate to the card or container\n- use `show-percent` when the number itself is important\n- pair circle progress with clear labels outside the ring in data-dense views\n- verify slot or center-label capabilities from source before building custom\n  gauges\n\n## Related Demos\n\n- `src/demo-pages/component/progress/index.vue`\n\n## Drill-Down Paths\n\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/circle-progress/src/circle-progress.vue`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/circle-progress/src/circle-progress.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/circle-progress/src/instance.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/circle-progress.scss`\n\n## Evidence Status\n\n- Demo confirmed:\n  - `src/demo-pages/component/progress/index.vue`\n- Source paths mapped:\n  - `components/circle-progress/src/circle-progress.vue`\n  - `components/circle-progress/src/circle-progress.ts`\n- Still verify in source:\n  - exact percent range assumptions\n  - whether center content or label customization is supported\n"
