    "uri": "tuniao://tnui/components/count-scroll",
    "name": "count-scroll",
    "description": "tn-count-scroll Count Scroll",
    "mimeType": "text/markdown",
    "content": "# tn-count-scroll Count Scroll\n\n---\ncategory: display\ntitle: Count Scroll / 数字滚动\ncomponent-dir: count-scroll\nprimary-tags:\n  - tn-count-scroll\nrelated-tags: []\nstatus: stable\nsource-dir: node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/count-scroll\nstyle-source:\n  - node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/count-scroll.scss\ndemo-pages:\n  - src/demo-pages/component/count-scroll/index.vue\n---\n\n## Component Role\n\n`tn-count-scroll` is a rolling-number display that animates digit changes as a\nslot-machine style count transition.\n\n## Best Fit Scenarios\n\n- dashboards with attention-grabbing changing numbers\n- financial or statistic summaries\n- counters that update live and benefit from per-digit motion\n\n## Avoid Using It For\n\n- precise progress timing\n- giant walls of changing numbers\n- accessibility-critical displays where motion may distract\n\n## Recommended Repo Usage\n\n```vue\n<tn-count-scroll value=\"7548\" />\n```\n\n## Key Capabilities\n\n### Value Format\n\n- `value` as string input\n- demo shows integers\n- demo also shows decimals and thousands separators\n\n### Visual Controls\n\n- `text-color`\n- `font-size`\n\n## Boundary With Similar Components\n\n- use `count-scroll` when the visual effect is per-digit rolling\n- use `count-to` for direct numeric interpolation from one value to another\n- use plain text when the number changes infrequently and motion adds no value\n\n## AI Usage Notes\n\n- format the value string upstream if separators or decimals are required\n- reserve rolling motion for a small number of prominent metrics\n- verify update performance on frequently changing data\n- inspect source before relying on extremely large or negative numbers\n\n## Related Demos\n\n- `src/demo-pages/component/count-scroll/index.vue`\n\n## Drill-Down Paths\n\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/count-scroll/src/count-scroll.vue`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/count-scroll/src/count-scroll.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/count-scroll/src/instance.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/count-scroll.scss`\n\n## Evidence Status\n\n- Demo confirmed:\n  - `src/demo-pages/component/count-scroll/index.vue`\n- Source paths mapped:\n  - `components/count-scroll/src/count-scroll.vue`\n  - `components/count-scroll/src/count-scroll.ts`\n- Still verify in source:\n  - exact accepted value formats\n  - performance characteristics for frequent updates\n"
