    "uri": "tuniao://tnui/components/count-to",
    "name": "count-to",
    "description": "tn-count-to Count To",
    "mimeType": "text/markdown",
    "content": "# tn-count-to Count To\n\n---\ncategory: display\ntitle: Count To / 数字过渡\ncomponent-dir: count-to\nprimary-tags:\n  - tn-count-to\nrelated-tags: []\nstatus: stable\nsource-dir: node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/count-to\nstyle-source:\n  - node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/count-to.scss\ndemo-pages:\n  - src/demo-pages/component/count-to/index.vue\n---\n\n## Component Role\n\n`tn-count-to` is an animated number transition component that interpolates from\none value to another.\n\n## Best Fit Scenarios\n\n- KPI or revenue counters\n- statistics cards\n- animated transitions between old and new numeric values\n- showing magnitude change more smoothly than a hard text swap\n\n## Avoid Using It For\n\n- per-digit rolling displays better suited to `count-scroll`\n- countdown timers\n- progress where a bar or ring is more readable\n\n## Recommended Repo Usage\n\n```vue\n<tn-count-to start=\"0\" end=\"6745\" />\n```\n\n## Key Capabilities\n\n### Number Transition Model\n\n- `start`\n- `end`\n- `decimals`\n- `thousands-separator`\n\n### Visual Controls\n\n- `text-color`\n- `font-size`\n\n## Boundary With Similar Components\n\n- use `count-to` for start-to-end interpolation\n- use `count-scroll` for rolling digit animation\n- use `count-down` for decreasing time-based numbers\n\n## AI Usage Notes\n\n- keep start and end values explicit when animating backend updates\n- use decimals only when the number truly needs precision\n- format large numbers with separators for readability\n- verify duration and easing support from source before standardizing KPI cards\n\n## Related Demos\n\n- `src/demo-pages/component/count-to/index.vue`\n\n## Drill-Down Paths\n\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/count-to/src/count-to.vue`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/count-to/src/count-to.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/count-to/src/instance.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/count-to.scss`\n\n## Evidence Status\n\n- Demo confirmed:\n  - `src/demo-pages/component/count-to/index.vue`\n- Source paths mapped:\n  - `components/count-to/src/count-to.vue`\n  - `components/count-to/src/count-to.ts`\n- Still verify in source:\n  - exact animation duration defaults\n  - handling of negative values and rapid prop changes\n"
