    "uri": "tuniao://tnui/components/date-time-picker",
    "name": "date-time-picker",
    "description": "tn-date-time-picker Date Time Picker",
    "mimeType": "text/markdown",
    "content": "# tn-date-time-picker Date Time Picker\n\n---\ncategory: form\ntitle: Date Time Picker / 日期时间选择器\ncomponent-dir: date-time-picker\nprimary-tags:\n  - tn-date-time-picker\nrelated-tags: []\nstatus: stable\nsource-dir: node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/date-time-picker\nstyle-source: []\ndemo-pages:\n  - src/demo-pages/component/date-time-picker/index.vue\n---\n\n## Component Role\n\n`tn-date-time-picker` is a specialized popup picker for date, year-month, time,\nand datetime selection.\n\n## Best Fit Scenarios\n\n- choose structured date or time values through a wheel-like popup\n- forms that need one specific date/time field\n- cases where a compact popup is preferable to an embedded calendar\n- standardized temporal input without free text parsing\n\n## Avoid Using It For\n\n- large calendar-range exploration\n- multi-date selection across many days\n- fully custom locale or calendar rules without source verification\n\n## Recommended Repo Usage\n\n```vue\n<tn-date-time-picker\n  v-model=\"dateValue\"\n  v-model:open=\"showPicker\"\n  mode=\"datetime\"\n/>\n```\n\n## Key Capabilities\n\n### Picker Modes\n\n- `mode=\"date\"`\n- `mode=\"yearmonth\"`\n- `mode=\"time\"`\n- `mode=\"datetime\"`\n\n### Range And Format Controls\n\n- `v-model:open`\n- `min-time`\n- `max-time`\n- `format`\n\n## Boundary With Similar Components\n\n- use `date-time-picker` for compact popup-based temporal input\n- use `calendar` when users need to read or choose from a visible calendar grid\n- use `picker` only for generic option columns, not domain-specific temporal\n  selection\n\n## AI Usage Notes\n\n- separate open-state and selected value state\n- pick the mode that matches the field data contract before wiring validation\n- use `format` only when the page needs a specific output representation\n- verify accepted input and output formats from source before normalizing API\n  payloads\n\n## Related Demos\n\n- `src/demo-pages/component/date-time-picker/index.vue`\n\n## Drill-Down Paths\n\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/date-time-picker/src/date-time-picker.vue`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/date-time-picker/src/date-time-picker.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/date-time-picker/src/types.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/date-time-picker/src/instance.ts`\n\n## Evidence Status\n\n- Demo confirmed:\n  - `src/demo-pages/component/date-time-picker/index.vue`\n- Source paths mapped:\n  - `components/date-time-picker/src/date-time-picker.vue`\n  - `components/date-time-picker/src/date-time-picker.ts`\n  - `components/date-time-picker/src/types.ts`\n- Still verify in source:\n  - exact formatting token support\n  - locale handling and emitted events\n"
