    "mimeType": "text/markdown",
    "content": "# tn-lazy-load Lazy Load\n\n---\ncategory: layout\ntitle: Lazy Load / 懒加载\ncomponent-dir: lazy-load\nprimary-tags:\n  - tn-lazy-load\nrelated-tags: []\nstatus: stable\nsource-dir: node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/lazy-load\nstyle-source:\n  - node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/lazy-load.scss\ndemo-pages:\n  - src/demo-pages/component/lazy-load/index.vue\n---\n\n## Component Role\n\n`tn-lazy-load` is a lazy-rendered image/content loader that delays actual asset\nloading until the item approaches the viewport.\n\n## Best Fit Scenarios\n\n- long image feeds\n- waterfall or list pages with many remote images\n- performance-sensitive pages with repeated image cards\n\n## Avoid Using It For\n\n- single hero images already above the fold\n- upload flows where the image is local and immediately visible\n- content that must always render instantly\n\n## Recommended Repo Usage\n\n```vue\n<tn-lazy-load :src=\"item\" />\n```\n\n## Key Capabilities\n\n### Core Use\n\n- lazy source loading through `src`\n- suited to repeated image lists\n\n### Performance Pattern\n\n- primarily reduces initial rendering and image fetch pressure on long pages\n\n## Boundary With Similar Components\n\n- use `lazy-load` for deferred image/content rendering\n- use `photo-album` for gallery layout\n- use plain image tags when the list is small and performance is not an issue\n\n## AI Usage Notes\n\n- pair with repeated list rendering rather than isolated images\n- keep container dimensions stable to avoid layout shift\n- verify placeholder and error behaviors from source if the page depends on\n  graceful fallbacks\n- inspect integration with scroll containers before using it outside normal page\n  flow\n\n## Related Demos\n\n- `src/demo-pages/component/lazy-load/index.vue`\n\n## Drill-Down Paths\n\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/lazy-load/src/lazy-load.vue`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/lazy-load/src/lazy-load.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/lazy-load/src/types.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/lazy-load/src/instance.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/lazy-load.scss`\n\n## Evidence Status\n\n- Demo confirmed:\n  - `src/demo-pages/component/lazy-load/index.vue`\n- Source paths mapped:\n  - `components/lazy-load/src/lazy-load.vue`\n  - `components/lazy-load/src/lazy-load.ts`\n  - `components/lazy-load/src/types.ts`\n- Still verify in source:\n  - placeholder, error, and retry behavior\n  - intersection or scroll-observer strategy details\n"
