    "uri": "tuniao://tnui/components/list",
    "name": "list",
    "description": "tn-list-item List",
    "mimeType": "text/markdown",
    "content": "# tn-list-item List\n\n---\ncategory: display\ntitle: List / 列表项\ncomponent-dir: list\nprimary-tags:\n  - tn-list-item\nrelated-tags: []\nstatus: stable\nsource-dir: node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/list\nstyle-source:\n  - node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/list.scss\ndemo-pages:\n  - src/demo-pages/component/list/index.vue\n---\n\n## Component Role\n\n`list` is currently represented in repo demos through `tn-list-item`, a\ncontent-row component for list-style cells and settings rows.\n\n## Best Fit Scenarios\n\n- settings rows\n- information list cells\n- navigable list items with right icons\n- grouped rows with shared border and radius styling\n\n## Avoid Using It For\n\n- heavy card layouts that need richer container composition\n- action-first UI where a button is clearer\n- drag, reorder, or swipe patterns that need `swipe-action`\n\n## Recommended Repo Usage\n\n```vue\n<tn-list-item right-icon=\"right\">关于图鸟</tn-list-item>\n```\n\n## Key Capabilities\n\n- `radius`\n- `right-icon`\n- `bottom-border`\n- `bottom-border-indent`\n- `font-size`\n- `bg-color`\n- `text-color`\n- `right-icon-color`\n- `custom-class`\n- custom content through the default slot\n\n## Boundary With Similar Components\n\n- compare with buttons when the row triggers an action rather than displaying a\n  navigable cell\n- compare with `swipe-action` when side actions are required\n- compare with plain layout `view` containers when no list-cell styling or\n  affordance is needed\n\n## AI Usage Notes\n\n- use slot content when the row needs custom icon-and-text composition\n- prefer list items for settings-style navigation rows over manually styled\n  bordered `view` blocks\n- use `bottom-border-indent` only when grouped rows need indented separators\n\n## Related Demos\n\n- `src/demo-pages/component/list/index.vue`\n\n## Drill-Down Paths\n\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/list/src/list-item.vue`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/list/src/list-item.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/list/src/composables/*`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/list.scss`\n\n## Evidence Status\n\n- Demo confirmed:\n  - `src/demo-pages/component/list/index.vue`\n- Source paths mapped:\n  - `components/list/src/list-item.vue`\n  - `components/list/src/list-item.ts`\n- Still verify in source:\n  - whether the directory also exposes other list primitives used outside the\n    current demo\n  - exact slot and event surface\n"
