    "uri": "tuniao://tnui/components/loadmore",
    "name": "loadmore",
    "description": "tn-loadmore Loadmore",
    "mimeType": "text/markdown",
    "content": "# tn-loadmore Loadmore\n\n---\ncategory: display\ntitle: Loadmore / 加载更多\ncomponent-dir: loadmore\nprimary-tags:\n  - tn-loadmore\nrelated-tags: []\nstatus: stable\nsource-dir: node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/loadmore\nstyle-source:\n  - node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/loadmore.scss\ndemo-pages:\n  - src/demo-pages/component/loadmore/index.vue\n---\n\n## Component Role\n\n`tn-loadmore` is a list-footer status component for load-more, loading, no-more,\nand empty terminal states.\n\n## Best Fit Scenarios\n\n- infinite or paginated lists\n- list footers after the main content block\n- “loading more” feedback without a custom footer implementation\n- pages that need explicit no-more or empty-tail copy\n\n## Avoid Using It For\n\n- full-page loading states\n- top-of-page feedback bars\n- empty states for pages that have no list at all\n\n## Recommended Repo Usage\n\n```vue\n<tn-loadmore status=\"loading\" />\n```\n\nKeep the list state in page logic and let `tn-loadmore` only render the visual\nstatus.\n\n## Key Capabilities\n\n### Status Model\n\n- default load-more prompt\n- `status=\"loading\"`\n- `status=\"nomore\"`\n- `status=\"empty\"`\n\n### Customization\n\n- custom text map through `text`\n- `loading-icon-mode`\n- `loading-text`\n- `loading-icon`\n- size presets and custom numeric size\n- `color`\n\n## Boundary With Similar Components\n\n- use `loadmore` only at the tail of lists or feeds\n- use `loading` for generic spinner use\n- use `empty` when the whole page or list has no data from the start\n\n## AI Usage Notes\n\n- map backend paging states to the `status` field explicitly\n- keep custom copy short and action-aware\n- use `empty` state only when the list container still exists and the footer is\n  the right place for the message\n- verify exact status enum names in source before extracting a shared list-state\n  helper\n\n## Related Demos\n\n- `src/demo-pages/component/loadmore/index.vue`\n\n## Drill-Down Paths\n\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/loadmore/src/loadmore.vue`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/loadmore/src/loadmore.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/loadmore/src/instance.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/loadmore.scss`\n\n## Evidence Status\n\n- Demo confirmed:\n  - `src/demo-pages/component/loadmore/index.vue`\n- Source paths mapped:\n  - `components/loadmore/src/loadmore.vue`\n  - `components/loadmore/src/loadmore.ts`\n- Still verify in source:\n  - exact text override contract and defaults\n  - expose API or additional icons beyond demo-covered modes\n"
