    "uri": "tuniao://tnui/components/photo-album",
    "name": "photo-album",
    "description": "tn-photo-album Photo Album",
    "mimeType": "text/markdown",
    "content": "# tn-photo-album Photo Album\n\n---\ncategory: display\ntitle: Photo Album / 相册\ncomponent-dir: photo-album\nprimary-tags:\n  - tn-photo-album\nrelated-tags: []\nstatus: stable\nsource-dir: node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/photo-album\nstyle-source:\n  - node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/photo-album.scss\ndemo-pages:\n  - src/demo-pages/component/photo-album/index.vue\n---\n\n## Component Role\n\n`tn-photo-album` is an image gallery layout component for showing several images\nin a compact tiled arrangement.\n\n## Best Fit Scenarios\n\n- post or feed image groups\n- gallery previews\n- compact multi-image card bodies\n\n## Avoid Using It For\n\n- image upload flows\n- carousels with one active slide at a time\n- massive masonry layouts that need column balancing\n\n## Recommended Repo Usage\n\n```vue\n<tn-photo-album :data=\"imageListData\" :max=\"9\" />\n```\n\n## Key Capabilities\n\n### Gallery Controls\n\n- `data` for the image list\n- `max` to limit how many images render\n- `column` to control images per row\n\n## Boundary With Similar Components\n\n- use `photo-album` for small gallery-style image groups\n- use `swiper` for focus-based slide browsing\n- use `water-fall` when the layout is a larger masonry feed\n\n## AI Usage Notes\n\n- choose `max` based on the target card density\n- keep image aspect ratios in mind when mixing album layouts with text blocks\n- use `column` to tune compactness for small screens\n- verify preview-click behavior from source if tapping images must open a\n  viewer\n\n## Related Demos\n\n- `src/demo-pages/component/photo-album/index.vue`\n\n## Drill-Down Paths\n\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/photo-album/src/photo-album.vue`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/photo-album/src/photo-album.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/photo-album/src/instance.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/photo-album.scss`\n\n## Evidence Status\n\n- Demo confirmed:\n  - `src/demo-pages/component/photo-album/index.vue`\n- Source paths mapped:\n  - `components/photo-album/src/photo-album.vue`\n  - `components/photo-album/src/photo-album.ts`\n- Still verify in source:\n  - exact preview interaction behavior\n  - layout rules when image count exceeds `max`\n"
