    "content": "# tn-tabbar Tabbar\n\n---\ncategory: navigation\ntitle: Tabbar / 底部导航栏\ncomponent-dir: tabbar\nprimary-tags:\n  - tn-tabbar\nrelated-tags:\n  - tn-tabbar-item\nstatus: stable\nsource-dir: node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/tabbar\nstyle-source:\n  - node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/tabbar.scss\n  - node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/tabbar-item.scss\ndemo-pages:\n  - src/demo-pages/component/tabbar/index.vue\n---\n\n## Component Role\n\n`tabbar` is the bottom-navigation family for switching between top-level\napplication sections.\n\n## Best Fit Scenarios\n\n- primary application navigation\n- persistent bottom navigation with badges\n- fixed navigation bars with safe-area handling\n- navigation menus with active icons and color states\n\n## Avoid Using It For\n\n- inline content switching inside a page; use `tabs` instead\n- wizard-like progress steps; use `steps` instead\n- light segmented selection; use `subsection` instead\n\n## Recommended Repo Usage\n\n```vue\n<tn-tabbar v-model=\"currentTabbarIndex\" fixed>\n  <tn-tabbar-item text=\"基础\" icon=\"assign\" active-icon=\"assign-fill\" />\n</tn-tabbar>\n```\n\n## Family Structure\n\n- parent tag: `tn-tabbar`\n- child tag: `tn-tabbar-item`\n- selected state lives on the parent `v-model`\n- the parent controls layout, fixed behavior, animation, and switch rules\n- the child controls icon, active icon, badge, disable state, and bulge style\n\n## Key Capabilities\n\n### Parent Controls\n\n- `v-model` for active tab index\n- `height`, `icon-size`, and `font-size`\n- `inactive-color`\n- `before-switch` for switch interception\n- `switch-animation`\n- `fixed`\n- `frosted`\n- `safe-area-inset-bottom`\n- `z-index`\n\n### Child Controls\n\n- `text`\n- `icon`\n- `active-icon`\n- `active-color`\n- `badge`\n- `badge-config`\n- `disabled`\n- `bulge`\n\n## Boundary With Similar Components\n\n- use `tabbar` for app-level navigation, not for page-internal category\n  switching\n- compare with `tabs` when both show peer choices but only one should behave as\n  global navigation\n- compare with list or card navigation when bottom persistence is not required\n\n## AI Usage Notes\n\n- keep the active index on `tn-tabbar`\n- use `fixed` and `safe-area-inset-bottom` intentionally when the bar should\n  remain visible near device bottom edges\n- use `before-switch` when some tabs require permission checks or blockers\n- use item badges and `bulge` instead of manually composing floating icons\n\n## Related Demos\n\n- `src/demo-pages/component/tabbar/index.vue`\n\n## Drill-Down Paths\n\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/tabbar/src/tabbar.vue`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/tabbar/src/tabbar.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/tabbar/src/tabbar-item.vue`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/tabbar/src/tabbar-item.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/tabbar/src/composables/*`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/tabbar.scss`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/tabbar-item.scss`\n\n## Evidence Status\n\n- Demo confirmed:\n  - `src/demo-pages/component/tabbar/index.vue`\n- Source paths mapped:\n  - `components/tabbar/src/tabbar.vue`\n  - `components/tabbar/src/tabbar-item.vue`\n- Still verify in source:\n  - exact event names beyond `v-model` changes\n  - item slot support or extra per-item props not shown in the demo\n"
