    "uri": "tuniao://tnui/components/title",
    "name": "title",
    "description": "tn-title Title",
    "mimeType": "text/markdown",
    "content": "# tn-title Title\n\n---\ncategory: display\ntitle: Title / 标题\ncomponent-dir: title\nprimary-tags:\n  - tn-title\nrelated-tags: []\nstatus: stable\nsource-dir: node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/title\nstyle-source:\n  - node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/title.scss\ndemo-pages:\n  - src/demo-pages/basic/title/index.vue\n---\n\n## Component Role\n\n`tn-title` is a styled section-title component for page subsections, decorated\nheadings, and title-plus-subtitle blocks.\n\n## Best Fit Scenarios\n\n- section headings inside a page body\n- cards or modules that need a stronger title treatment\n- decorated heading styles without custom CSS\n- title and subtitle combinations\n\n## Avoid Using It For\n\n- top navigation headers handled by `navbar`\n- inline labels inside forms\n- long paragraphs or rich-text descriptions\n\n## Recommended Repo Usage\n\n```vue\n<tn-title title=\"图鸟UI\" />\n```\n\n## Key Capabilities\n\n### Title Modes\n\n- plain title\n- `mode=\"dot\"`\n- `mode=\"vLine\"`\n- `mode=\"hLine\"`\n- `mode=\"subTitle\"`\n- `mode=\"transparent\"`\n\n### Visual Controls\n\n- size presets and custom numeric size\n- `color`\n- `assist-color`\n- `sub-title`\n\n## Boundary With Similar Components\n\n- use `title` for section headings inside content\n- use `navbar` for the page header area\n- use `tag` or `badge` for small metadata, not headline text\n\n## AI Usage Notes\n\n- prefer `tn-title` when the section heading needs more than plain text\n- keep mode choice aligned with the visual hierarchy of the page\n- use subtitle mode for explanatory secondary text rather than inserting extra\n  views around the title\n- verify exact slot support from source if you need custom heading markup\n\n## Related Demos\n\n- `src/demo-pages/basic/title/index.vue`\n\n## Drill-Down Paths\n\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/title/src/title.vue`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/title/src/title.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/components/title/src/instance.ts`\n- `node_modules/@tuniao/tnui-vue3-uniapp/theme-chalk/src/title.scss`\n\n## Evidence Status\n\n- Demo confirmed:\n  - `src/demo-pages/basic/title/index.vue`\n- Source paths mapped:\n  - `components/title/src/title.vue`\n  - `components/title/src/title.ts`\n- Still verify in source:\n  - exact title/subtitle slot behavior\n  - additional assist-line or transparent mode nuances\n"
